This Will be the classic game Pong!

The game works with two players each controlling a rectangular slider block which they will use to stop a ball from hitting their wall. You get a point by getting the ball to hit the other player's wall.


This will be done in C++



		***Controls***

	Player One
	
Up - 'w'
Down - 's'

	Player Two

Up - 'Up Arrow'
Down - 'Down Arrow'
